  <brief_title>Impact of Fluoride Vanish Application in Dental Prevention for Elderly</brief_title>
  <acronym>VERNIS</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Impact of Fluoride Vanish Application in Dental Prevention Among Institutionalised Elderly People</official_title>
