  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study questions the interest of fluoride varnish dental application in preventing tooth
      decay in a population of institutionalised elderly people.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Application of fluoride varnish on one side of the mandibles (left or right, randomly
      selected) in a population of institutionalised elderly people.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
